			<div class="article-correspondence layout-item fill-pattern-light">
		<div class="layout-item-intro">
			<h2>Correspondence</h2>
			<a class="xsmall link-alt" href="https://www.thesunmagazine.org/letter-to-the-editor">Write a Letter to the Editor&nbsp;&#9656;</a>
		</div>

		<div id="article-correspondences" class="correspondences correspondences-collapsed">
								<div class="block-correspondence" id="1886">
		<blockquote class="quote-2">
			<p>I empathized as I read Ann Bauer&rsquo;s &ldquo;<a href="/article/462">The Drunkard&rsquo;s Gait</a>&rdquo; [April 2004], but I disagreed with her insistence that &ldquo;alcohol is not the problem.&rdquo; Her wondering why her alcoholic husband remained symptomatic with no ongoing treatment is akin to wondering why a diabetic gets sick when he doesn&rsquo;t monitor his blood sugar. The sad truth is, most of us alcoholics don&rsquo;t get the treatment we need.</p>

<p>I winced when Bauer &ldquo;ordered a Corona and tried to drink at least half of it&rdquo; in an effort to show her potentially-at-risk kids that &ldquo;it&rsquo;s not the alcohol.&rdquo; I spent the first forty years of my life trying to prove that it&rsquo;s not the alcohol &mdash; this after my father, my grandfather, and four aunts and uncles died from this affliction. Alcoholism is a family disease. It <em>is</em> the alcohol, and the alcoholism.</p>
							<p class="quote-2-author">Herby Bell<br>Santa Cruz, California</p>
					</blockquote>
	</div>

					</div>

			</div>
    
		<div class="article-correspondence-cta">
		<div class="cta cta-l1" data-url="https://www.thesunmagazine.org/letter-to-the-editor">
			<div class="cta-intro">
				<h5 class="cta-title alt-ff">Thinking about writing us a letter?</h5>
				<p class="cta-text">Give in to the temptation. We love getting mail. <br><span class="xsmall">(Of course, we reserve the right to edit.)</span></p>
			</div>
			<a href="https://www.thesunmagazine.org/letter-to-the-editor" class="cta-button b b-4 b-padding-tight small" data-label="Write Us A Letter!">Write Us A Letter!</a>
		</div>
	</div>
	

